{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01RWwUnJxQVZKQtn5rVdNvEF","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've found and read all the sound-related files. Here's the complete content of each file:\n\n---\n\n## 1. **soundStore.ts** \n**/Users/markus/baustelle/projects/agents-in-the-office/agents-in-the-office/.chief/worktrees/sound-packs-patchbay/src/stores/soundStore.ts**\n\nComprehensive sound management store using Pinia. Key features:\n- **Config Management**: Saves/loads sound configuration from `~/.agents-in-the-office/sound-packs/config.json`\n- **Pack Scanning**: Discovers sound packs directory structure (pack → category → audio files)\n- **Playback Engine**: Plays audio for agent events with:\n  - Per-category cooldowns\n  - Global volume control\n  - Track-level enable/disable\n  - Buffer caching with AudioContext API\n- **Session Pack Assignment**: Maps each session to a preferred sound pack (randomly selected from active packs)\n- **Types**: `TrackConfig`, `SoundConfig`, `PackInfo`\n- **AGENT_EVENT_TYPES**: Complete list of 16 event types that can trigger sounds\n\n---\n\n## 2. **SoundsDialog.vue**\n**/Users/markus/baustelle/projects/agents-in-the-office/agents-in-the-office/.chief/worktrees/sound-packs-patchbay/src/components/SoundsDialog.vue**\n\nFull-featured sound management UI component. Key features:\n- **Global Controls**: Enable/disable, global volume, cooldown slider\n- **Pack Management**:\n  - Create new packs with inline form\n  - Import packs from ZIP files (drag-drop or file picker)\n  - Right-click context menu (rename, duplicate, delete)\n- **Category Management**: \n  - Expandable categories for each event type\n  - Bulk enable/disable per category\n  - Info popovers with event descriptions\n- **Track Management**:\n  - Add audio files to categories\n  - Delete individual tracks\n  - AudioPlayer component for preview/control\n- **UI Components**: Uses `AudioPlayer.vue` and `PackContextMenu.vue` subcomponents\n- **EVENT_DESCRIPTIONS**: Human-readable descriptions for all 16 event types\n\n---\n\n## 3. **drivers/types.ts**\n**/Users/markus/baustelle/projects/agents-in-the-office/agents-in-the-office/.chief/worktrees/sound-packs-patchbay/src/drivers/types.ts**\n\nCore type definitions for the agent driver system:\n\n**AgentEventType enum (16 types)**:\n```typescript\n'session_start' | 'session_end' | 'prompt_submit' | 'tool_start' | 'tool_end' \n| 'turn_end' | 'permission_wait' | 'subagent_start' | 'subagent_end' \n| 'idle_notification' | 'elicitation_wait' | 'auth_success' | 'worktree_create' \n| 'worktree_remove' | 'teammate_idle' | 'task_completed'\n```\n\n**Key Interfaces**:\n- `AgentEvent`: `{ sessionId, timestamp, type: AgentEventType, agentType, payload }`\n- `NpcHandle`: NPC control interface (gotoObject, enterRoom, leaveRoom, wander, showBubble, etc.)\n- `ActivityMessage`: `{ id, timestamp, side, text, fullText }`\n- `SubagentInfo`: `{ subagentSessionId, parentSessionId, nativeAgentId, transcriptPath }`\n- `NpcCommand`: Union type for NPC movement/interaction commands\n\n---\n\n## 4. **types.ts** \n**/Users/markus/baustelle/projects/agents-in-the-office/agents-in-the-office/.chief/worktrees/sound-packs-patchbay/src/types.ts**\n\nMap/tilemap type definitions (not directly sound-related, but referenced for tile/collision system):\n- Tile/AutoTile/CellValue types\n- Layer metadata\n- Interactive objects with directional collision\n- Spawn points\n- Object types (door, computer, books, coffee, plant, desk, chair)\n- Directional collision bitmask constants (DIR_UP, DIR_RIGHT, DIR_DOWN, DIR_LEFT)\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\nThe sound system is fully implemented with:\n- **16 event types** that trigger sounds (all defined in both soundStore and types.ts)\n- **Pinia store** (`soundStore`) handling persistence, playback, and session pack assignment\n- **Vue dialog** (`SoundsDialog.vue`) providing full pack management UI\n- **Type safety** via `AgentEventType` union type\n- **Lazy AudioContext** initialization on first playback\n- **Per-track configuration** (enable/disable, volume)\n- **Session-aware playback**: each agent session is assigned a preferred sound pack\n- **Cooldown system**: prevents audio spam with configurable delays per category"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: aefe8e45c11d57ecd (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 81770\ntool_uses: 8\nduration_ms: 19481</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"75b2882c-830d-4bff-b8cd-d257d75432f2","uuid":"fb942766-b0fb-455a-8148-1f1625262df8","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the sound-related files in /Users/markus/baustelle/projects/agents-in-the-office/agents-in-the-office/.chief/worktrees/sound-packs-patchbay/. Find and read:\n1. Any soundStore file (src/stores/soundStore.ts or similar)\n2. SoundsDialog component\n3. Any sound-related types or interfaces\n4. The AgentEventType enum/values\n\nReturn the full content of each file found.","agentId":"aefe8e45c11d57ecd","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've found and read all the sound-related files. Here's the complete content of each file:\n\n---\n\n## 1. **soundStore.ts** \n**/Users/markus/baustelle/projects/agents-in-the-office/agents-in-the-office/.chief/worktrees/sound-packs-patchbay/src/stores/soundStore.ts**\n\nComprehensive sound management store using Pinia. Key features:\n- **Config Management**: Saves/loads sound configuration from `~/.agents-in-the-office/sound-packs/config.json`\n- **Pack Scanning**: Discovers sound packs directory structure (pack → category → audio files)\n- **Playback Engine**: Plays audio for agent events with:\n  - Per-category cooldowns\n  - Global volume control\n  - Track-level enable/disable\n  - Buffer caching with AudioContext API\n- **Session Pack Assignment**: Maps each session to a preferred sound pack (randomly selected from active packs)\n- **Types**: `TrackConfig`, `SoundConfig`